title: Uncovering heterogeneity in infected E. Huxleyi cultures by morphological profiling of imaging flow cytometry data
description: Imaging flow cytometry data of Emiliana huxleyi infected with its specific large double-stranded DNA Emiliana huxleyi virus. Cells were stained with single-molecule fluorescence in situ hybridization to measure viral infection and metabolic activity.
